Dedupe PRELOADABLE_BACKENDS_LIBS' sanei_usb.lo against libdll_preload.la (sane-backends 1.4.0)

Upstream bug: backend/Makefile.am's libsane_la_LIBADD pulls in
`libdll_preload.la` (whose own LIBADD already bundles ../sanei/sanei_usb.lo,
$(USB_LIBS), $(XML_LIBS) -- see libdll_preload_la_LIBADD a few lines above)
*and* the separate blanket PRELOADABLE_BACKENDS_LIBS list, which lists
../sanei/sanei_usb.lo again. libtool inlines a convenience library's own
LIBADD objects wherever that .la is linked in, so sanei_usb.lo's ~30 symbols
(_sanei_usb_open, etc.) end up in the libsane.la link line twice, and both
Apple's default ld and ld-classic reject that as duplicate symbols.

Upstream's own comment admits the blanket list is wrong in general:

    # FIXME: This is using every possibly needed library and dependency
    # when the user is using any PRELOADABLE_BACKENDS, irrespective of
    # what backends are preloaded.  It should include what is needed by
    # those backends that are actually preloaded.

This patch does the minimal fix for the concrete duplicate: drop the
../sanei/sanei_usb.lo line from PRELOADABLE_BACKENDS_LIBS, since it is
already supplied (once) via libdll_preload.la, which is unconditionally
part of libsane_la_LIBADD regardless of which backends are preloaded. It
does not otherwise touch the "kitchen sink" behavior the FIXME describes.

Applies to both backend/Makefile.am (source) and backend/Makefile.in (the
tarball's pre-generated file, which is what autotools actually build from
in this environment -- see Vendor/README.md for why both are patched by
hand instead of regenerating via autoreconf).

--- a/backend/Makefile.am
+++ b/backend/Makefile.am
@@ -2025,7 +2025,6 @@
 if preloadable_backends_enabled
 PRELOADABLE_BACKENDS_LIBS = \
     ../sanei/sanei_config2.lo \
-    ../sanei/sanei_usb.lo \
     ../sanei/sanei_scsi.lo \
     ../sanei/sanei_pv8630.lo \
     ../sanei/sanei_pp.lo \
--- a/backend/Makefile.in
+++ b/backend/Makefile.in
@@ -4224,7 +4224,6 @@
 # those backends that are actually preloaded.
 @preloadable_backends_enabled_TRUE@PRELOADABLE_BACKENDS_LIBS = \
 @preloadable_backends_enabled_TRUE@    ../sanei/sanei_config2.lo \
-@preloadable_backends_enabled_TRUE@    ../sanei/sanei_usb.lo \
 @preloadable_backends_enabled_TRUE@    ../sanei/sanei_scsi.lo \
 @preloadable_backends_enabled_TRUE@    ../sanei/sanei_pv8630.lo \
 @preloadable_backends_enabled_TRUE@    ../sanei/sanei_pp.lo \
